                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/17752</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from"
                            >Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Querétaro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-04-04T13:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 4, 1916, 1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>25. In reply to Department’s April 3, 5 p.m. Generals Carranza and Obregon and
                    Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs in the country for day. Could not
                    ascertain. Foreign Office whether appropriate instruction Chihuahua authorities
                    have been issued. Do not believe they have been. Insisted to Subsecretary of
                    State for Foreign Affairs that promise given March 30 be fulfilled. Promised by
                    Amador that promise stated my March 30, 3 p.m., was given. Saw Cabrera who
                    stated that customs officers border have been instructed to expedite entry
                    adequate supplies. Cabrera also promised investigation as to appropriate
                    instructions Chihuahua authorities.</p>
                <p>Believe reason for delay reluctance General Carranza himself to give any official
                    recognition to this use Northwestern Railway by American forces.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
